snippet.title: Slot Quest: Alice in Wonderland
snippet.description:
Game play suited for gamers of all skill levels from experienced to beginner, startling music and astounding graphics will be able to embark into this immersive world of fantastic adventures of Slot Quest: Alice in Wonderland.  The task at hand asks you to restore four famous stories that are being maliciously rewritten by four evil characters. Defeat the evil villains, including the Queen of Hearts, Wicked Witch, Mr. Hyde, and the Evil Dragon. 
http://www.bigbirdgames.com/pccard/item/slot-quest-alice-in-wonderland
